review_blob: i  love this beer so much.i go back to kuhnhenn all the time rarely available.good thing all there beer is great.

the farmhouse ale is great.so much flavor and not heavy at all.this is a great beginers beer.i live 20 minutes from dexter,michigan where jolly pumkin is located.its store is open on friday only 12-6pm worth the trip stock up.there is no bar though.
